Create Slicers and Scorecards: Stages 3-7 13

1. Select the slicer visual

2. Add Sex column into the fields

3. In the format column go to the general Tab  and input the following specifics X Position 609, Width 176, height 89

4. On the Items Tab : Custom Font Color #605E5C, Text Size 10, Font Segoue UI

5. On the Title Tab ; Rename title to Sex, Background Color #5B855C

6. On the Border Tab : Choose Custom Color #224624


1. Select the Scorecard Visual

2.. Drag and Drop the Measure Total Attacks into the fields tab

3. In the format tab, format data label to Arial Black,  text size 20

4.Slide Title on, rename to Total Attacks, background color : Custom color 5B855C

5. On the General Tab change X position 765, Width 176
